Creative and educational game for children that will help your child spend time with an electronic device effectively. Let your child feel like a real artist. The app includes coloring activity which is friendly to the youngest as well as drawing lessons intended to develop fine motor skills. Also, the app contains pictures on different topics which will entertain your child with fascinating sounds and funny characters. The following is waiting for you:

- 9 topic packs with 135 pages;
- Easy coloring for children;
- Drawing lessons;
- Creativity development.

The app is designed for children of preschool age and also suitable for boys and girls 2- 4 years old. All the activities were developed with participation of experts in the field of children education and include such educational elements as developing of fine motor skills and logic. Have fun!

"English Conversation Practice" is the helpful app to practice english conversation for everyone. With a lot of english conversations categorized in different levels, you can strengthen your english listening and speaking skills perfectly. This app also includes many useful resources for real-life situations and examination.

You can find everything you need for learning English by downloading this app: English Conversation, Listening, Speaking, English Idioms and Phrases, Vocabulary, Single Sentences, Short Stories, Essays, English Grammar, Daily News, Games and Tests, IELTS, TOEIC, etc.

Most stuff in the app has audio supported.

Learning English has never been so simple.

Main features:
- 1000+ conversations with American native speakers. All conversations are separated into many real-life topics.
-  Practice conversation;
- Sentence Builder Game;
- 800+ English short stories;
- 1200+ daily phrasal verbs;
- 3000+ most commonly used sentences;
- 3000+ most commonly used vocabulary;
- 3000+ IELTS Academic vocabulary; 
- 15000+ English Idioms and Phrases;
- Evaluate your pronunciation;
- Effective Learning: helps you improve Vocabulary (capacity and pronunciation).
- Vocabulary Listening Test;
- Hangman vocabulary game;
- English Grammar Test;
- Completed English idioms and phrases dictionary;
- Completed list of irregular verbs with audio supported;
- Free lessons from BBC Leaning English (British pronunciation) and VOA Learning English (American pronunciation);
- Spotlight English Talk lessons;
- Evaluate your pronunciation easily with voice recognition;
- Online Dictionary integrated to help users find word's meaning fast;
